data.description: Welcome to this spacious home that seamlessly combines comfort, style, and functionality. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the inviting and open concept living space, featuring laminate wood-like flooring that enhances the warmth and charm of the main living areas on the main floor. The formal dining room, thoughtfully situated off the entry, boasts an abundance of natural and recessed lighting, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen is a true culinary delight. It showcases granite counters, a tasteful tile backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances, which include a convenient built-in microwave. The addition of a corner pantry ensures ample storage space for all your kitchen essentials. The living room is a highlight, with its high-slanted ceiling that adds a sense of grandeur. It also offers easy access to the backyard, allowing for a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor living. A half bath nearby provides added convenience for guests. On the main floor, you'll find the primary suite, a private retreat that includes an ensuite bath equipped with dual vanity sinks, a relaxing garden tub, and a spacious walk-in shower and a walk-in closet.  For added convenience, a laundry room is also located on the main floor, making everyday chores simple. Heading upstairs, you'll discover a versatile loft area that could serve as a second living room or a game room, catering to your lifestyle needs. In addition to the loft, there are three secondary bedrooms on this level, ensuring plenty of space for everyone. A well-appointed full bathroom completes the upper level.  This home also boasts the added benefit of a water softener, enhancing your water quality and overall living experience.  The appeal of this property extends beyond its walls, as it is situated in a vibrant community that offers an array of amenities. From a clubhouse and exercise-fitness facilities to a refreshing pool and tennis courts, this neighborhood truly has it all. Nature enthusiasts will appreciate the walking trails, while an onsite lifestyle director ensures a lively and engaged community. The amenities list goes on to include an amphitheater, basketball court, beach entry pool, food truck station, junior Olympic lap pool, slide tower, waterfall with sun bench, must-use field, open-air pavilion, outdoor kitchens, and a playground & picnic area. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning house your new home, where every feature and amenity has been thoughtfully designed to enhance your quality of life.
